Mapper2d adapted to growable travmap. Also added travmap_grow_strategy
functor class (so far only implemented as never_grow). Adusted
TraversabilityMap::Autogrow() to accept a grow_notify functor which
will make it possible to know when the travmap has grown (useful
e.g. in asl-mplan to determie when to grow the E* C-space). Improved
flexgrid somewhat, should bring those changes into E* as well.

